    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I think I'd lean towards no. Like with `%run` or `import`, I'd consider the file a separately parsed module, so I wouldn't inherit future flags from there to the interactive environment.\n\nWe also don't share future flags from startup files (just checked), or from files specified by `exec_files` in config (IIRC). We _do_ from `exec_lines` in config. I think that supports my view.\n"
  },
